459
00:24:19.330 --> 00:24:20.682
¿Adónde quieres ir?

460
00:24:28.257 --> 00:24:29.316
Vaya.

461
00:24:30.551 --> 00:24:31.569
Sip.

462
00:24:32.177 --> 00:24:33.195
Aquí es.

463
00:24:33.971 --> 00:24:35.031
Es...

464
00:24:36.224 --> 00:24:38.243
Es más grande que la última.

465
00:24:39.394 --> 00:24:43.455
